1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:05,000
-= CHD字幕组 =-
校订翻译：dxch dahongying

2
00:00:33,825 --> 00:00:36,326
你以为你一天的工作很糟糕吗？
You think you've had a bad day at work?

3
00:00:37,203 --> 00:00:38,412
我觉得我比你惨
I think I got you beat.

4
00:00:43,126 --> 00:00:44,168
这不是我
That's not me.

5
00:00:46,921 --> 00:00:48,380
不 这是我的搭档
Nope, that's my partner.

6
00:00:58,391 --> 00:00:59,433
去你的！
Suck it!

7
00:01:00,351 --> 00:01:01,602
我在这儿
There I am.

8
00:01:01,686 --> 00:01:02,700
三四天前
Three or four days ago,

9
00:01:02,721 --> 00:01:04,146
我不知道有这个世界的存在
I didn't know this world existed.

10
00:01:07,692 --> 00:01:09,443
但三四天前
But three or four days ago,

11
00:01:09,527 --> 00:01:11,653
我还不是冥界警局的一份子
I wasn't in the Rest In Peace Department.

12
00:01:12,828 --> 00:01:17,070
片名：冥界警局

13
00:01:20,210 --> 00:01:23,323
三、四天前…

14
00:02:08,878 --> 00:02:10,712
一里之外我就听到你过来了
I heard you coming a mile away.

15
00:02:11,381 --> 00:02:14,133
奇怪 法国女孩都该骑在波士顿最棒的男人身上
Look at this, French girl gets the drop on Boston's finest.

16
00:02:14,676 --> 00:02:16,176
你却骑在我身上啊 对吗？
You got the drop on me, huh?

17
00:02:16,302 --> 00:02:17,928
我现在感觉自己像个天才
But I feel like a genius right now.

18
00:02:18,054 --> 00:02:19,680
如果您打算要更好的
I couldn't have planned this better.

19
00:02:19,848 --> 00:02:22,224
好吧 天才 有棵桔树倒在后园里
Well, genius, there is an orange tree in the backyard.

20
00:02:22,559 --> 00:02:24,226
怎么会如此？
How did that get there?

21
00:02:27,230 --> 00:02:29,398
是的 后园里有颗桔树
Yeah, there is an orange tree in the backyard.

22
00:02:29,566 --> 00:02:30,774
真奇怪
How weird.

23
00:02:33,528 --> 00:02:34,903
我不知道它是怎么到这儿来的
I don't know how it got here.

24
00:02:35,071 --> 00:02:36,405
我也不知道
Me neither.

25
00:02:36,573 --> 00:02:38,240
你知道它象征繁荣吗？
You know it's a symbol of prosperity, don't you?

26
00:02:38,408 --> 00:02:39,616
没有 我从来没听过
No, I've never heard that.

27
00:02:39,742 --> 00:02:40,993
是真的 问问佛罗里达州的人们
It is, yeah. Ask anyone in Florida.

28
00:02:41,077 --> 00:02:42,327
不 你疯了吗
No, you're crazy.

29
00:02:42,412 --> 00:02:44,454
它可能无法活过冬天
This tree is never gonna make it through the winter.

30
00:02:45,248 --> 00:02:47,332
可能有人无法活过冬天
We might not make it through the winter

31
00:02:47,417 --> 00:02:49,710
因为这房子里很冷！
in this freezing little house!

32
00:02:49,794 --> 00:02:52,421
但我就爱我们的冷房子
I love our freezing little house.

33
00:02:52,547 --> 00:02:53,714
你也爱 对吗？
You do, do you?

34
00:02:53,798 --> 00:02:55,924
是吗？
Yeah?

35
00:02:56,593 --> 00:02:58,260
你别无所求了吗？
But don't you want more?

36
00:02:58,678 --> 00:02:59,845
你总是担心钱不够
You're always worried about money.

37
00:03:00,013 --> 00:03:01,597
你不是想要好房子吗？好车子吗？
Don't you want a real house? A car?

38
00:03:01,848 --> 00:03:04,516
我才不担心钱 是你担心
I don't worry about money, you do.

39
00:03:04,684 --> 00:03:06,935
我需要的一切都在这里
I have everything I need right here.

40
00:03:07,103 --> 00:03:09,563
我的丈夫陪伴着我
My husband, with me.

41
00:03:11,191 --> 00:03:12,941
你将会一直拥有的
Well, you'll always have that.

42
00:03:22,285 --> 00:03:23,285
我得去上班了
I gotta go to work.

43
00:03:23,453 --> 00:03:25,120
我会告诉你什么时候你可以上班
I'll tell you when you can go to work.

44
00:03:25,288 --> 00:03:27,331
真的吗？
Really?

45
00:03:36,633 --> 00:03:39,051
当心扭到脚 爱你 亲爱的
Watch that ankle. I love you, baby.

46
00:03:43,305 --> 00:03:44,388
再见 我也爱你
Bye. Love you.

47
00:04:00,031 --> 00:04:02,074
什么时候我照片和奖杯才会在陈列柜中
Got my picture in a trophy case, I see.

48
00:04:02,158 --> 00:04:04,034
看看这个 可以永垂不朽了
Look at that. Already immortalized.

49
00:04:04,202 --> 00:04:07,246
那需要天时地利 我还能说什么？
Right place, right time. What can I say?

50
00:04:07,413 --> 00:04:09,081
- 嘿 鲍比  - 你好
- Hey, Bobby. - Hey.

51
00:04:09,791 --> 00:04:12,417
墨菲！天啊 加件浴衣吧
Murph! Jesus, get a robe or something.

52
00:04:12,585 --> 00:04:14,503
那围巾可支撑不了
You're asking too much of that towel.

53
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:17,923
- 早上好 伙计  - 早上好
- Morning, partner. - Morning.

54
00:04:18,299 --> 00:04:19,841
嘿 伙计们
Hey, guys.

55
00:04:20,009 --> 00:04:21,593
记得周一员工聚会上见
Love to have you at the union meeting Monday.

56
00:04:21,761 --> 00:04:23,178
不 不！上帝啊 墨菲
No, no! Sweet Jesus, Murphy.

57
00:04:23,346 --> 00:04:25,305
我会射爆那东西
I will shoot that thing.

58
00:04:25,473 --> 00:04:26,556
真令人受不了
That's pretty devastating.

59
00:04:26,724 --> 00:04:29,142
这可能令我对工作留下创伤
It's gonna be a while before I get that image out.

60
00:04:29,978 --> 00:04:32,145
嘿 你那份怎么样了？
Hey, what did you do with yours?

61
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,024
- 我埋了  - 真的吗？
- I buried it. - Really?

62
00:04:36,567 --> 00:04:37,600
没开玩笑？
I thought you were joking about that.

63
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:39,152
不会有更糟的主意了
But it's not the worse idea.

64
00:04:39,237 --> 00:04:41,530
它是黄金 你却埋了它 对吧？
It's gold, you bury it. Right?

65
00:04:44,284 --> 00:04:45,742
听着 鲍比
Listen, Bobby.

66
00:04:46,536 --> 00:04:47,536
我要退出
I'm out.

67
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:50,080
退出？
You're out?

68
00:04:50,290 --> 00:04:51,290
听着
Look.

69
00:04:52,625 --> 00:04:53,875
这对你不会有任何影响
Nothing has to change for you.

70
00:04:54,043 --> 00:04:55,000
做你想做的
You do whatever you want,

71
00:04:55,018 --> 00:04:56,670
对于我 它已结束了
but I'm putting mine in evidence. It's done.

72
00:04:56,921 --> 00:04:59,631
老弟 我说我会处理好
Nicky, I said I would move it for us.

73
00:04:59,716 --> 00:05:00,966
我会搞定一切的
I'll take care of everything.

74
00:05:01,092 --> 00:05:02,301
我不是说这些 鲍比
That's not what I'm talking about, Bobby.

75
00:05:02,385 --> 00:05:05,262
我是说今早她已怀疑我有问题
I'm talking about the way she looked at me this morning,

76
00:05:05,346 --> 00:05:06,346
我早估到
I knew.

77
00:05:06,431 --> 00:05:08,406
听着 我们只是去那里打击毒品的
Look, we went in there to make a drug bust,

78
00:05:08,881 --> 00:05:09,975
仅此而已
which we did.

79
00:05:10,059 --> 00:05:12,102
我们没想到天上竟然掉黄金
We didn't expect this gold to fall into our laps.

80
00:05:12,186 --> 00:05:14,021
我们又不是故意的 但它就这么发生了
We weren't looking for it, but it happened.

81
00:05:14,522 --> 00:05:17,733
我看出来了 你是为了朱莉娅做的
The way I see it, you do it for Julia.

82
00:05:17,817 --> 00:05:20,027
为了你们的未来 这很简单
For your future together. It's simple.

83
00:05:20,111 --> 00:05:22,362
不 她很幸福 我不想拿她的幸福冒险
No, she's happy. I'm not gonna risk that.

84
00:05:24,365 --> 00:05:26,033
对不起 伙计
I'm sorry, buddy.

85
00:05:30,663 --> 00:05:31,705
你说得对
You're right.

86
00:05:33,082 --> 00:05:35,208
但我讨厌你说得对
I hate it when you're right.

87
00:05:36,252 --> 00:05:38,045
我们要是上交东西的话
We gotta turn the whole thing in.

88
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:40,881
买游艇就没希望了
There goes the speedboat.

89
00:05:41,049 --> 00:05:42,174
听着
Look.

90
00:05:42,842 --> 00:05:44,885
别担心 我不会出卖你的
You don't have to worry, I'm not wagging my finger at you.

91
00:05:44,969 --> 00:05:46,178
你做你想做的
You do whatever you want to do.

92
00:05:46,262 --> 00:05:48,388
不 这仍令我不安
No, it's bothering me, too.

93
00:05:49,182 --> 00:05:50,807
那就让我们一起变成老穷鬼
So, let's grow old and poor together.

94
00:05:50,892 --> 00:05:53,435
听着 发现加尔萨了 还得到个地址
Listen up, we got Garza. We got an address.

95
00:05:53,936 --> 00:05:56,104
等等 发现加尔萨？你真的肯定是他吗？
Wait, you got Garza? You got actual eyes on him?

96
00:05:56,189 --> 00:05:57,856
有线人供出了他所有的冰毒交易
An informant gave up his whole meth operation.

97
00:05:57,940 --> 00:05:59,274
他就在那儿 他跑不掉了
He's there, we got him.

98
00:05:59,734 --> 00:06:01,943
好吧 我们开工吧 伙计
Okay, we're in business, partner.

99
00:06:02,028 --> 00:06:04,071
再为陈列柜再加些新照片了
Get another picture in the trophy case.

100
00:06:10,328 --> 00:06:12,996
你知道我们等待加尔萨出错等了多久吗？
You know how long we've been waiting for Garza to slip up.

101
00:06:13,081 --> 00:06:14,800
这家伙是个毒贩 警察杀手
This guy's a meth dealer, a cop killer.

102
00:06:14,824 --> 00:06:15,957
有30多个手下
He's got 30 guys with him.

103
00:06:16,042 --> 00:06:17,167
抓住他不容易
He's not gonna go easy.

104
00:06:17,251 --> 00:06:19,878
现在 准备好了 听听激动人心的
Now, stand by for inspiring,

105
00:06:19,962 --> 00:06:22,047
来自侦探鲍比・海耶斯的有启发性的训话
motivating words from Detective Bobby Hayes.

106
00:06:22,131 --> 00:06:23,882
我们今天不要吃枪子 如何？
How about we don't get shot today?

107
00:06:24,258 --> 00:06:26,343
很好的建议 你是一个好警察
That's great advice. You're a good cop.

108
00:06:26,427 --> 00:06:28,887
侦探海耶斯的意见是我们都不要中弹
Detective Hayes advises we should avoid getting shot.

109
00:06:28,971 --> 00:06:31,431
还有 所有人都应该戴上他的魔力手链
And also, everybody should put their charm bracelets on now.

110
00:06:31,516 --> 00:06:33,308
嘿 那是我祖母的
Hey, that's my grandmother's

111
00:06:33,393 --> 00:06:35,060
圣克里斯多夫手链啊 你个白痴
Saint Christopher medal, jackass.

112
00:06:35,144 --> 00:06:36,228
真可爱
It's adorable.

113
00:06:36,312 --> 00:06:37,604
我依赖它的保护
I wear it for protection.

114
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:40,023
它的保护？这个才能挡子弹
It's for protection? Well, this stops bullets.

115
00:06:40,108 --> 00:06:42,234
你戴那个是约不到女孩子的
Yours stops you from getting dates.

116
00:07:02,547 --> 00:07:03,547
上吧！
Let's go!

117
00:07:04,424 --> 00:07:06,341
行动！上吧！去！
Move it! Move it! Let's go!

118
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:19,896
跟上我 我们会先进入
On my lead. Let's put them on their heels.

119
00:07:19,981 --> 00:07:22,524
注意安全 好吗？
Be safe, will you?

120
00:07:36,038 --> 00:07:37,205
开门 开门
Knock, knock.

121
00:07:41,544 --> 00:07:42,836
警察！
Police officer!

122
00:07:55,975 --> 00:07:57,517
把东西带走
Take the stuff out of here.

123
00:07:57,685 --> 00:07:59,603
快打包！快打包！
Bag the stuff! Bag the stuff!

124
00:08:08,946 --> 00:08:10,322
我看到加尔萨
I see Garza.

125
00:08:32,553 --> 00:08:33,803
他在楼梯上！
He's on the catwalk!

126
00:08:48,528 --> 00:08:51,279
该死的！他从南面窗口逃走了
Damn it! Garza's out the south window.

127
00:08:53,115 --> 00:08:54,115
天啊！
Jesus!

128
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,909
- 这真危险啊  - 你干什么呢？
- That was close. - What the hell are you doing?

129
00:08:55,993 --> 00:08:57,035
你差点打到我了
You almost got me.

130
00:08:57,912 --> 00:08:59,037
但是
But,

131
00:08:59,747 --> 00:09:01,581
我不会让你上交黄金
I can't let you turn that gold in.

132
00:09:02,458 --> 00:09:03,542
什么？
What?

133
00:09:15,012 --> 00:09:16,930
“我的丈夫陪伴着我”
My husband, with me.

134
00:11:29,825 --> 00:11:30,825
监察员

135
00:11:31,190 --> 00:11:32,649
艰难的一天
Tough day.

136
00:11:34,610 --> 00:11:36,528
这是正常的 起初是会有点吃惊的
It's normal to be a little tongue-tied at first.

137
00:11:36,696 --> 00:11:39,948
我想让你明白我是来帮你的
I want you to know that I'm here to help you.

138
00:11:40,449 --> 00:11:43,118
我也坐过那把椅子
I've sat in that chair.

139
00:11:43,285 --> 00:11:45,328
所以放松点
So take your time.

140
00:11:45,663 --> 00:11:46,830
慢慢来了解吧
Ease into it.

141
00:11:47,623 --> 00:11:49,040
我要了解什么？
Ease into what?

142
00:11:50,459 --> 00:11:53,545
来吧 天才 我知道你能行
Come on, genius. I know you can get there.

143
00:11:57,967 --> 00:11:59,134
这是一个笑话吗？
This is a joke.

144
00:12:00,010 --> 00:12:02,137
很滑稽
Hilarious.

145
00:12:03,973 --> 00:12:05,098
我死了吗？
I'm dead?

146
00:12:05,474 --> 00:12:07,058
说实话 当一个黑警察
Let's be honest, being a dirty cop

147
00:12:07,143 --> 00:12:09,602
是一个被当面射杀的比例较高的职业
is one of the higher shot-in-the-face-percentage jobs.

148
00:12:10,688 --> 00:12:11,813
我不是黑警察
That's not who I am.

149
00:12:11,897 --> 00:12:13,898
真的吗 帅哥？
Really, pretty boy?

150
00:12:13,983 --> 00:12:17,402
当你朝着审判之路行进时感觉如何？
How did it feel as you were headed towards Judgment?

151
00:12:17,486 --> 00:12:18,528
舒服吗？
Comfortable?

152
00:12:18,988 --> 00:12:20,447
你觉得自己够光荣能上天堂？
Feel like you were bound for glory?

153
00:12:20,531 --> 00:12:22,949
还是有点担心会下地狱？
Or were you a little worried that you were going down?

154
00:12:25,202 --> 00:12:26,494
我是这么认为的
I thought so.

155
00:12:27,329 --> 00:12:28,663
你很幸运 尼克
You're lucky, Nick.

156
00:12:29,081 --> 00:12:30,947
你有我们想要的技能
You have skills that we want.

157
00:12:30,947 --> 00:12:32,751
所以我们给你一个选择
So we're giving you a choice.

158
00:12:32,835 --> 00:12:35,879
你可以选择受审判
You can take your chances with Judgment,

159
00:12:36,714 --> 00:12:37,714
或
or,

160
00:12:40,009 --> 00:12:42,010
你可以加入RIPD
you can join the R.I.P.D.

161
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:45,430
什么RIPD？
The R.I.P.D?

162
00:12:45,514 --> 00:12:47,307
冥界警察局
Rest In Peace Department.

163
00:12:47,892 --> 00:12:49,976
我懂了 好名字
I get it. It's cute.

164
00:12:51,854 --> 00:12:52,979
简单地说
Simply put,

165
00:12:53,355 --> 00:12:57,317
我们专捉那些设法逃脱审判的死人
we find dead people that have managed to escape Judgment.

166
00:12:58,736 --> 00:13:02,489
送他们回到属于他们的地方
We ship them off back down to where they belong.

167
00:13:02,573 --> 00:13:04,449
这合约是100年期限
The tour is 100 years.

168
00:13:04,533 --> 00:13:05,200
如果你答应了
If you say yes,

169
00:13:05,230 --> 00:13:07,452
我们可以把你送回波士顿 你的老家
we'll send you back down to Boston, your home turf.

170
00:13:07,536 --> 00:13:08,828
我答应
I'll do it.

171
00:13:09,705 --> 00:13:12,207
这行不通的
That's not gonna work.

172
00:13:12,374 --> 00:13:13,708
什么行不通？我说了我加入
What's not gonna work? I said I'm in.

173
00:13:13,876 --> 00:13:14,800
我知道你在想什么
I know what you're thinking.

174
00:13:14,886 --> 00:13:16,419
你耍赖 你想要回以前的生活
You got rooked, you want your old life back.

175
00:13:16,504 --> 00:13:17,504
你想要朱莉娅
You want Julia.

176
00:13:17,671 --> 00:13:20,000
不是 你问我能否加入
No. You asked me to help you,

177
00:13:20,099 --> 00:13:21,800
我说我能加入
and I'm here to help.

178
00:13:22,384 --> 00:13:24,928
你真的以为我看不穿你吗？
You really don't think I can read you?

179
00:13:28,224 --> 00:13:31,559
这里有关于你的一切资料
I know everything there is to know about you.

180
00:13:32,228 --> 00:13:34,521
千万别浪费这个机会 尼克
Don't squander this opportunity, Nick.

181
00:13:34,605 --> 00:13:36,773
而且我肯定你会需要一封好的
I know for a fact you can use a good

182
00:13:36,899 --> 00:13:39,067
推荐信去参加审判日的 对吧？
recommendation on Judgment Day, okay?

183
00:13:39,944 --> 00:13:42,362
我觉得我提起了你的兴趣了
I think you're smelling what I'm selling.

184
00:13:44,156 --> 00:13:45,323
还有其他问题吗？
Any more questions?

185
00:13:48,244 --> 00:13:49,577
这是史提利丹乐团的什么歌？
