You were right about the job, Roy.

938
01:00:29,167 --> 01:00:30,500
我们应该回去了
We gotta get back out there.

939
01:00:30,835 --> 01:00:33,378
不-可-能
"Sus-pen-dato."

940
01:00:33,671 --> 01:00:35,881
如果想要我回去 他们应该要来求我
If they want me back, they're gonna have to beg.

941
01:00:36,049 --> 01:00:38,175
我不要留下来等死 你呢？
I'm not gonna take this lying down. You?

942
01:00:39,385 --> 01:00:40,886
