I never noticed any kind of "soul stank."

954
01:01:07,622 --> 01:01:11,750
我听说某种稀有护身符能掩盖阴气
I heard talk of a rare kind of artifact that could mask it.

955
01:01:12,251 --> 01:01:14,419
像除臭剂 灵魂香水
Like a spiritual deodorant.

956
01:01:14,754 --> 01:01:17,422
定是他随身佩戴的东西
It would be something he carried with him all the time.

957
01:01:18,299 --> 01:01:20,425
祖母的圣克里斯多夫项链
Like Grandma's Saint Christopher medal.

958
01:01:20,593 --> 01:01:21,802
就是那个了
That'd do her.

959
01:01:26,057 --> 01:01:27,766
让我们令那混蛋现形吧
Let's go pop the son of a bitch.

960
01:01:48,496 --> 01:01:49,788
你知道要做什么？
Do you know what to do?

961
01:01:49,956 --> 01:01:52,624
是的 我等了很长一段时间了
Yeah. I've been waiting a long time for this.

962
01:01:52,792 --> 01:01:54,543
你等了很长时间吗？
You've been waiting a long time?

963
01:01:54,627 --> 01:01:57,087
你知道腐尸花了多少年要做成这件事吗？
Do you know how many years Deados have been trying to pull this off?

964
01:01:57,171 --> 01:01:58,380
3000年
Three thousand.

965
01:01:58,464 --> 01:02:02,134
这些废物没有一个能收集起所有的黄金
Not one of those jag-offs could get all that gold together,

966
01:02:02,301 --> 01:02:03,760
直到我出现
until me.

967
01:02:05,471 --> 01:02:07,806
RIPD根本不知道是什么重击了他们
R.I.P.D. is not gonna know what hit them.

968
01:02:08,599 --> 01:02:10,684
现在你亲自去惹点麻烦
Now, go find yourself some trouble.

969
01:02:10,977 --> 01:02:12,519
非常乐意
My pleasure.

970
01:02:24,949 --> 01:02:25,991
你好 朱莉娅
Hey, Julia.

971
01:02:26,075 --> 01:02:27,868
我想和你谈谈
I need to talk to you.

972
01:02:27,952 --> 01:02:29,870
我碰到了很奇怪的事情
Something really strange happened to me.

973
01:02:30,997 --> 01:02:32,080
怎么回事呢？
What's going on?

974
01:02:32,165 --> 01:02:33,665
我昨晚在跑道上
I was at the track last night,

975
01:02:33,750 --> 01:02:35,917
你还记得葬礼上的那个家伙吗？
and do you remember that guy at the funeral?

976
01:02:36,085 --> 01:02:37,252
小个子的中国佬？
The little Chinese guy?

977
01:02:37,837 --> 01:02:38,920
大叫大闹的那个？
The one who was yelling?

978
01:02:39,005 --> 01:02:40,714
慢慢说 慢慢说 深吸一口气
Slow down, slow down. Take a deep breath.

979
01:02:40,798 --> 01:02:42,382
我不知道 我觉得
I don't know. Somehow, I feel like

980
01:02:42,467 --> 01:02:45,430
那像是尼克试图跟我说话的感觉
it's Nick who's trying to talk to me.

981
01:02:47,096 --> 01:02:48,305
好吧
Okay.

982
01:02:49,056 --> 01:02:50,724
我知道这听起来很疯狂
I know it sounds crazy.

983
01:02:50,850 --> 01:02:53,018
我知道你想念他 我也想念他
I know you miss him. I miss him, too.

984
01:02:54,353 --> 01:02:56,104
我认为现在你不该独自去面对
I don't think you should be alone right now.

985
01:02:56,606 --> 01:02:58,356
我去接你 一起吃个午饭
I'm gonna come pick you up, and I'm gonna take you to lunch

986
01:02:58,441 --> 01:03:00,901
我们可以好好谈谈
and we could talk about everything.

987
01:03:01,277 --> 01:03:02,652
好吗？
All right?

988
01:03:05,364 --> 01:03:06,531
好吧
Okay.

989
01:03:07,658 --> 01:03:08,950
好的 谢谢你帮助我
All right. Thank you for this.

990
01:03:09,285 --> 01:03:11,745
应该的  回头见
Absolutely. I'll see you later.

991
01:03:29,889 --> 01:03:31,431
你负责前面 我绕到后面
Take the front. I'll go around back.

992
01:03:31,516 --> 01:03:33,058
看我的
Works for me.

993
01:03:49,659 --> 01:03:50,700
鲍比・海耶斯？
Bobby Hayes?

994
01:03:51,577 --> 01:03:52,619
什么事？
Yeah?

995
01:03:52,703 --> 01:03:54,746
我要问你一些问题
I need to ask you a few questions

996
01:03:54,914 --> 01:03:56,998
关于印度式粘土烤箱的问题
involving a tandoori clay oven.

997
01:03:57,166 --> 01:03:59,626
宝贝 你可以问任何你想要的事情
Sweetheart, you can ask me anything you want.

998
01:04:09,679 --> 01:04:11,096
请不要拘束
Make yourself comfortable.

999
01:04:16,435 --> 01:04:18,770
喝一杯怎么样？
How about a little drinky-poo?

1000
01:04:19,438 --> 01:04:21,940
好的 让我润润嘴
Sure. I'll wet my beak.

1001
01:04:22,108 --> 01:04:23,441
马上就来
Coming right up.

1002
01:04:32,243 --> 01:04:34,244
你在找这个吗？
Are you looking for this?

1003
01:04:34,787 --> 01:04:36,454
身手不错啊
Nice moves,

1004
01:04:36,539 --> 01:04:37,581
尼克
Nick.

1005
01:04:39,292 --> 01:04:41,293
这外表不佳啊
Hey, tough look to pull off.

1006
