I'm getting used to it.

1007
01:04:44,797 --> 01:04:46,047
你知道那只是个交易而已
You know, it was just business.

1008
01:04:46,173 --> 01:04:47,424
试试再动一下
Make a move, please.

1009
01:04:47,508 --> 01:04:48,508
放松点 尼克
Easy, Nick.

1010
01:04:50,636 --> 01:04:52,554
“在圣灰星期三”
"It's late on Ash Wednesday."

1011
01:04:52,638 --> 01:04:54,556
我们能跳过那一步 罗伊
We can skip that part, Roy.

1012
01:04:56,142 --> 01:04:57,642
摘掉圣克里斯托弗项链
Take off the Saint Christopher's medal.

1013
01:04:58,311 --> 01:04:59,394
快
Now.

1014
01:05:00,396 --> 01:05:01,479
好吧
Okay.

1015
01:05:34,180 --> 01:05:35,513
很强大的阴气
Powerful stank.

1016
01:05:36,849 --> 01:05:38,350
黄金何在 死鬼？
Where's the gold, dead man?

1017
01:05:38,684 --> 01:05:39,684
检查这里的热水器
Check the water heater.

1018
01:05:40,519 --> 01:05:41,853
这里有超级警察在
Freaking super cop, here.

1019
01:05:48,319 --> 01:05:50,111
好吧 上马鞍
All right, saddle up.

1020
01:05:52,990 --> 01:05:54,699
我们要带你回去
We're gonna ride you in.

1021
01:05:56,243 --> 01:05:57,285
