01:06:27,149 --> 01:06:29,484
我们在一起做什么与你无关
What we got together is none of your damn business.

1028
01:06:29,568 --> 01:06:31,152
剩余黄金在哪 海耶斯？
Where's the rest of the gold, Hayes?

1029
01:06:31,237 --> 01:06:33,613
明白我的意思了吗？他不会死心的
See what I mean? He won't let it die.

1030
01:06:35,366 --> 01:06:37,117
嘿 尼克 记得我中弹那事吗？
Hey, Nick, remember when I got shot?

1031
01:06:37,201 --> 01:06:39,494
