Wild guess, you didn't pull through?

1033
01:06:41,288 --> 01:06:43,081
被一名吸毒者杀死 去了地狱
Get killed by some junkie and go to hell

1034
01:06:43,165 --> 01:06:45,000
就因为我贪污小钱为了看脱衣舞娘跳舞吗？
because I took a little on the side to pay for lap dances?

1035
01:06:45,084 --> 01:06:46,835
不 我认为不会
No. I don't think so.

1036
01:06:46,919 --> 01:06:49,671
谁去决定我命运？我接受不了
Who gets to make that call? I don't accept it.

1037
01:06:49,755 --> 01:06:50,839
