Hey, let me ask you something.

1038
01:06:50,923 --> 01:06:53,174
你认为永恒的惩罚是什么 海耶斯？
What do you think eternal punishment is gonna be like, Hayes?

1039
01:06:53,592 --> 01:06:56,302
可以亲我的屁股
Hell can kiss my ass.

1040
