那这个也得登记
Then it gets booked,

1050
01:07:22,288 --> 01:07:25,540
还有我带来的那堆黄金
along with this gold that I brought in.

1051
01:07:26,417 --> 01:07:28,300
听好了 娃娃脸
That's right, doll face.

1052
01:07:28,310 --> 01:07:30,962
别管我那胆小鬼似的停职令
Despite my chicken-shit suspension.

1053
01:07:31,130 --> 01:07:34,200
