1068
01:08:11,504 --> 01:08:14,089
嘿 我们刚刚登记了跟这一样的东西
Hey, we just booked something just like this.

1069
01:08:14,173 --> 01:08:16,007
是的 在那里的篮子里
It's in the basket over there.

1070
01:08:19,512 --> 01:08:21,763
