1083
01:09:24,326 --> 01:09:25,493
全都在这儿吗？
It's all there?

1084
01:09:27,037 --> 01:09:28,037
接住！
Catch!

1085
01:09:28,122 --> 01:09:30,081
用所有手臂接住 来吧！
Fill up all these hands. Come on!

1086
01:09:32,585 --> 01:09:34,377
走了！走了！
Let's go! Let's go!

1087
01:09:46,265 --> 01:09:47,515
怎么了？
What's up?

1088
01:09:49,268 --> 01:09:50,602
安静
Peace.

1089
01:09:58,903 --> 01:10:00,111
冲洗
Flush it.

1090
01:10:02,281 --> 01:10:03,740
不！黄金！
No! The gold!

1091
01:10:08,787 --> 01:10:10,121
找你的 老板
Here, boss.

1092
01:10:10,456 --> 01:10:11,497
我都拿到了
I got it all.

